# SOP: Three-Plane Migration

1) Sandbox Plane
   - Put inputs in sandbox/inputs/
   - `make tri-run` then `make merge`
   - Review parent/fitness-report.json

2) Contracts & SBOM
   - Update contracts/*.capnp; add golden samples
   - `make gen-sbom && make sign && make verify`
   - `make contract-test`

3) Orchestrator Plane
   - `make hooks-install` (strict pre-push)
   - Policies in orchestrator/policies/
   - Keys in orchestrator/keys/ (offline)

4) Execution Plane
   - `make anchor`
   - `make promote` (if gates pass)

Rollback: revert to previous anchor; artifacts immutable.
